## Example Usage

```terraform
# Configure S3-compatible remote tier for ILM
resource "minio_ilm_tier" "s3_tier" {
  name     = "S3TIER"
  type     = "s3"
  bucket   = "remote-tier-bucket"
  prefix   = "minio-data/"
  region   = "us-east-1"
  endpoint = "s3.amazonaws.com"

  s3_config {
    access_key    = "AWS_ACCESS_KEY"
    secret_key    = "AWS_SECRET_KEY"
    storage_class = "STANDARD_IA"
  }
}
```

